```plantuml
@startuml shawntabrizi_Ethereum-Twitter-Bounty

package "Ethereum-Twitter-Bounty" {
    [TwitterBounty.sol] as TwitterBounty
    [TwitterOracle.sol] as TwitterOracle

    component "Web3.js" as Web3
    component "Truffle Framework" as Truffle {
        [truffle-config.js]
        [2_deploy_contracts.js]
        [TestTwitterBounty.js]
        [TestTwitterOracle.js]
        [TwitterBounty.json]
    }

    component "Frontend" as Frontend {
        [index.html]
        [app.js]
        [Bootstrap CSS]
    }

    component "Oracle Service" as OracleService {
        [Provable Things]
    }

    component "Ethereum Blockchain" as Ethereum {
        [Smart Contracts]
        [Events]
    }
}

TwitterBounty --> TwitterOracle : uses
TwitterBounty --> Ethereum : deploys to
TwitterOracle --> OracleService : fetches from
TwitterOracle --> Ethereum : stores on
Frontend --> Web3 : uses
Frontend --> Truffle : interacts with
Frontend --> TwitterBounty : interacts with
Truffle --> TwitterBounty : deploys
Truffle --> TwitterOracle : deploys
Web3 --> Ethereum : connects to

@enduml
```